---
title: Rustic Sicilian Penne with Zucchini, Peppers and Pine Nuts
description: Inspired by the classic Sicilian caponata dish, this rustic pasta is actually a twist on the French ratatouille. It's brought to life with briny olives and capers, and toasted pine nuts give the perfect finishing touch for extra texture and nuttiness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pennes-campagnardes-a-la-sicilienne-707f0d13.jpg
